replies.body:
I would disagree, you can play very poorly for 40-50 games, and make level 5 if your team wins or loses. There's no requirement to be good.

The first five levels are your, everyone gets a trophy level, while levels 6 and 7 remind you that you do have to earn things in life. It won't all be handed to you...

Level 6 and 7 require very high scores to earn tokens. This forces players to learn a champion's kit, learn the champion's role for the team, and to execute that role very well. You need to be better than average, you can't get carried into an S+ grade, it rewards GOOD players.

5100 IP you can purchase three champ shards and convert to 500 or 600 blue essence that you need. You will earn this IP learning your champion. It's a good system and rewarding way to spend your extra IP.

@RIOT you got this one right!
@RIOT Can we get old Shen back now?
